data.description: ** No Showings on home until 9-22-22** Nice Brick Home with lots of space. Hardwood floors in the living room with two book cases beside the fireplace. Seller is going to leave the TV & wall mount above fireplace. Kitchen has nice stainless appliances and will have a new floor installed. There is a dining room just off the kitchen with a backdoor to a patio. The kitchen has a small Eat-in area. Three bedrooms with 2 bathrooms. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet and a bathroom with tile floor and shower with seat. Other two bedrooms have balcony access off the front of the house. Hall Bathroom has an updated deep tub with ceramic wall tile. In the basement, there is a nice den with patio doors and a one car garage plus laundry room. Home has large concrete driveway, updated dimensional shingle roof and priced to move
